\">陈春花，管理界超级导师；冯卫东，投资界影响力人物。</span></strong><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">这是两位导师第一次亲临餐饮峰会现场，两位特地为餐饮朋友留出互动交流时间，千万别错过提问的机会哦。<img src=\"http://imgs.douguo.com/upload/keditor_img/20191127/20191127171632_41935.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; display: block; width: 690px;\"/></span></p><p helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" box-sizing:border-box=\"\" overflow-wrap:break-word=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 27px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\" p=\"\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">陈春花，著名组织文化管理与战略专家，被公认为“数字时代的管理创新思想家”。</span></strong><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">代表作有《共生》、《协同》等数十部。曾任新希望六和股份有限公司联席董事长兼首席执行官，开创管理学者到企业理论自洽实践的先河，数次获得《财富》“中国25位最具影响力商界女性领袖”、《财富》“中国最具影响力50位商界领袖 ”。</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" box-sizing:border-box=\"\" overflow-wrap:break-word=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 27px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\" p=\"\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">她的公众号《春暖花开》成为千万人的“管理课堂”，她联合创办知识实验室和“共生学习法”，帮助更多企业战略转型及持续发展，让管理研究创造更多社会价值。</span></p><p helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" box-sizing:border-box=\"\" overflow-wrap:break-word=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 27px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\" strong=\"\" span=\"\" img=\"\" src=\"http://imgs.douguo.com/upload/keditor_img/20191127/20191127171817_88637.jpg\" alt=\"\" br=\"\" p=\"\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">冯卫东，天图资本CEO/定位理论专家。</span></strong><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">拥有实业、咨询和投资的全面经验,对消费品牌成长规律有深入研究，著有“品牌非常道”系列文章和《升级定位24讲》，开创了“顾客价值配方”“品类三界论”“消费品企业六大竞争壁垒”等理论和实用工具，指导着天图的投资和投后服务。</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"/><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" box-sizing:border-box=\"\" overflow-wrap:break-word=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 27px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\" span=\"\" br=\"\" p=\"\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" box-sizing:border-box=\"\" overflow-wrap:break-word=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 27px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\" br=\"\" p=\"\"><span helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 27px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\" p=\"\" box-sizing:border-box=\"\" overflow-wrap:break-word=\"\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></span></p><p helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" box-sizing:border-box=\"\" overflow-wrap:break-word=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 27px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\" p=\"\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">近年来，不少创业者花重金投入餐饮设计，试图提高人气和影响力。然而设计对于餐饮而言，到底扮演什么角色呢？这次我们特别邀请到美学界三大才子——</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">对餐饮设计有着独特审美的吴国平、著名空间设计师陈林、</span></strong><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">黄记煌创始人黄耕，</span></strong><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">和我们共同探讨《餐饮之美》。</span></p><p helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" box-sizing:border-box=\"\" overflow-wrap:break-word=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 27px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\" span=\"\" img=\"\" src=\"http://imgs.douguo.com/upload/keditor_img/20191127/20191127172050_12721.jpg\" alt=\"\" p=\"\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">吴国平，</span></strong><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">外婆家创始人。</span></strong><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" box-sizing:border-box=\"\" overflow-wrap:break-word=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 27px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\" span=\"\" p=\"\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" box-sizing:border-box=\"\" overflow-wrap:break-word=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 27px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\" strong=\"\" span=\"\" p=\"\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">主持设计了玉玲珑、外婆家等知名餐厅。坚持“设计是为了获得消费者喜爱而非赢得设计界认同”的理念，因其操刀的餐厅设计风格极其精致，被江湖人称“精致餐厅的设计鼻祖”。</span></p><p helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" box-sizing:border-box=\"\" overflow-wrap:break-word=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 27px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\" br=\"\" p=\"\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">黄耕，黄记煌创始人 。</span></strong><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;</span></strong></p><p helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" box-sizing:border-box=\"\" overflow-wrap:break-word=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bott