em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\" span=\"\" p=\"\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; widows: 1; text-size-adjust: auto;\"><img src=\"http://imgs.douguo.com/upload/keditor_img/20191127/20191127172226_42517.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; display: block; width: 690px;\"/><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"/></span></span></strong></p><p helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" box-sizing:border-box=\"\" overflow-wrap:break-word=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 27px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\" strong=\"\" span=\"\" br=\"\" p=\"\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">洪明基</span></strong>，合兴集团控股有限公司行政总裁。</span></strong><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p